{"tid":1446083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣新方向］煲大黑警扮示威者","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:39:13.000Z","uid":201594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"967d25c829cf16ca8f935cf59f1944263ca25157","tid":1446083,"uid":201594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:43:32.000Z","msg":"既然依家有片有證據黑警扮示威者捉兄弟<br />\n咁就一於食住個勢 煲大佢 捉咁開心唔洗付出代價！？<br />\n<br />\n文宣可以將呢件事同之前發生過既衝突都拉埋一注黎講<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地既目標係中間游離派同輿輪！</span></strong><br />\n咁樣做可以將以前<span style=\"color: red;\">對我地不利既消息</span>全部扭轉鋒芒打返港共政權同黑警！又可以將一班淺黃拉返緊黎我地身邊！<br />\n<br />\n唔好放棄任何一個機會去進攻 文宣和理非係時候做野！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4749943bb955e331a3e66e37a5d274d24b818d89","tid":1446083,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"原來而家係 差佬內鬥<br />\n差佬扮示威者放火 堵路 打差佬"},{"pid":"a683de5dfb991051b7167b93a72963d57a0140ed","tid":1446083,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"417e72c086b9aaa458daa36010dec16ffc641817","tid":1446083,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:59:58.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"1dff70917fb3b372b40796dab379bf90b7c3ac9a","tid":1446083,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:01:30.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"4dc7aaaff45aac6642a2a1eb8501369737820786","tid":1446083,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:02:29.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"6d546593ef581eb16b87d52faf7e4bf1c1f0c007","tid":1446083,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:03:35.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"ae679b8d9e652c6f89813aaa55d53d7d86bd08c5","tid":1446083,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:04:12.00